== SAIL (Simple Assorion [User] Interface Layer) ==

This is mostly here to replace Flixel UI, and drop
the dependency count down to three (Lime, OpenFL,
and Flixel).

Unfortunately it adds another folder to the source
code but ultimately should be worth it as building
custom interfaces is probably easier.

===================================================

For those potentially cruising the source code:
SAIL doesn't contain any gameplay stuff, this is
entirely for the custom (chart) interface.

===================================================
